    <h5>Quick Ragu</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>1 jar of Vesper Brother's Foods Signature Tomato Sauce</li>
      <li>1 lb. of Fresh Ground Meat (Beef, or Turkey/Chicken for a healthy alternative)</li>
      <li>2 Tbsp of Extra Virgin Olive Oil</li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
      <li>Add Extra Virgin Olive Oil to a medium sized pan and sautee ground meat on medium-high heat until evenly browned and cooked through.</li>
      <li>Next, add 1 jar of Vesper Brother's Foods Signature Tomato Sauce and stir with cooked meat to combine.</li>
      <li>Let simmer 15 - 20 minutes.</li>
      <li>Toss with your favorite pasta for a quick and easy meal!</li>
    </ul>
